System Objectives

- Detect potential scam and phishing activities using AI-assisted analysis.
- Classify reported incidents based on scam categories and risk levels.
- Provide risk assessment scores for suspicious messages, links, and reports.
- Enable community members to submit and share scam reports.
- Identify scam-related keywords and suspicious patterns automatically.
- Generate threat intelligence insights through data analytics.
- Visualize scam trends and statistics through an interactive dashboard.
- Support administrators in monitoring and managing reported threats.
- Improve public awareness of emerging scams and phishing attacks.
- Maintain a centralized database of scam reports and analysis results.
